==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Enlistment
<hw>En*list"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
act or enlisting, or the state of being enlisted; voluntary enrollment
to serve as a soldier or a sailor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The writing by which an enlisted man is
bound.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Enlive</ent>⟦br⟧
